Invocation Name: d. shop assistant
des:
The skill acts as an intelligent assistant for inventory management by providing the following
Description about asset, Stock of asset, Availability of asset, Max booking days for asset, Different models for asset, Asset required to make certain project, Shelf location of asset etc. By invoking the d-shop assistant, the inventory management for d-shop becomes seamless
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
